    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-07-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-07-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="551"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d551">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Queen <persName type="from">Alexandra</persName> to President
                            <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-07-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 4, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The King is most grateful for kind sympathy; is, thank God, going on very
                    favorably now.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alexandra</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
